"version": "771.0", "version_code": 11664, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 66}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2412327085529357", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8379446065484066"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2309851355956647"}]}, "change_log": "## New Update v770.02\n\n## New Course: Lofoten Links\n\nRanked as the #24 golf course in the world by Golf Digest, Lofoten Links is located in the Arctic Circle of Norway and is one of the most unique and breathtaking courses you will find. In the summer months, golfers have the rare opportunity to play under the Midnight Sun - or witness the Northern Lights during the cooler seasons.\n\n## Scramble Update\n\n- You can now change captaincy at any time during a round.\n\n### Unrestricted Hit Order for Teams\n\n- Unrestricted Hit Order allows any player on a team to hit at anytime after the Captain selects the shot. \n- *Note: Unrestricted Hit Order is only for Hit Order within teams. The team furthest from the hole will still be up first.\n\n### Update to Standard Team Order\n\n- Player now has the ability to 'Defer Shot' to the next player, moving them to the back of the hit order.\n\n## Bug Fixes\n\n- Edge case where clubs could change length when teleporting while in Giant Mode.\n- The \"Hide the flag on the green\" setting was not working properly.\n- Scramble mode - If someone rejoined on the Back 9, players could get stuck in a turn, forcing everyone to leave the round.\n- GOLF+ Tour - Fixed an issue where the last hole of a round would not get counted right away, showing a DNF to the player, until it updated later on.", "